                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc> - Erasures: e.g., <locus target="#65va">65va</locus>, 81rb, 117rb.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e4"><desc>- Names of the days of
                           the week are written in recent hand: <locus from="9v" to="12r">9v-12r</locus>.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e5"><desc> - Scribbling: <locus target="#1va">1va</locus>,
                           67r, 130vb, 131r, </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e6"><desc> - Crude drawings: <locus target="#8v">8v</locus>,
                           9r, 10r, 36r, 130v.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e7">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- Coloured threads inserted in the corner of some
