                  <provenance>The name of the original donor Zawalda
                     Māryām has been erased throughout the Ms. and has been retained only on <locus target="#44vb">44vb</locus>. 
 According to Additio 4, the Ms. was
                     donated by Takla Māryām Walda Śǝllāse on behalf of the commemoration of
                     different persons. The names of Habta Śǝllāse and Gabra Madḫǝn were added to
                     the supplication formulas throughout the Ms. by the same hand as Additio
                     4.</provenance>
